Package battleship

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BattleButton
    Class the extends JButton, used as the individual squares for the boards.
    Board
    Class for the User board where they place their ships and keep track of the ship's status.
    GUI
    Frame for the battleship game, consisting of a pair of panels data between boards is transfered through this class.
    OppBoard
    Class for the opponent's board where user's target tand fire upon opponent's ships.
    Ship
    Ship class that extends JButton.
    SwitchPanel
    Panel used between turns so players on the same computer can't see each others board.
    TestBattleShip
    Class for testing battle ship.
    WinPanel
    Panel displayed when the game is over.
